casebody.data:
Tuesday, May 17, 1994

MOTION DOCKET

94-103. State v. D’Ambrosio.

Cuyahoga County, No. 56448. On motion to withdraw as counsel and request for appointment of counsel, and on pro se motion to withdraw counsel and appoint new counsel. Motions to withdraw granted and the Ohio Public Defender is appointed.

F.E. Sweeney, J., not participating.
